name: Batafuraiko (バタフライコ)
description: "Batafuraiko" (バタフライコ) is a playable arcade style game that fits in 1k of JavaScript code and the winner of JS1024 2021. This special NFT edition has a few small enhancements to better accommodate hic et nunc. For each edition sold $1 will be donated to the JS1024 Competition. 🦋
